ad_text: FRAYT Sponsored Work on your own schedule and earn extra income! We’re seeking cargo van drivers who are ambitious and dependable, to hire as independent contractors. FRAYT offers customers top notch service by matching their shipping needs with vehicles ready to pick up and deliver orders with our dash, scheduled, and multi-stop service offerings (a platform similar to Uber, but for business delivery). ⭐️ Apply here: https://bit.ly/FRAYTapply Or in the FRAYT Driver app! What are the main requirements? - Cargo Van, Sprinter Van, or Small Box Truck under 10,000 GVW - Vehicle 2002 or newer. Must be in good condition. - 21 or older to use the FRAYT platform. - Pay and Pass background check ($35 for MVR/Criminal). - Current License Plate Registration - Current Insurance Card or Declarations Page listing you as an insured driver - Valid Driver’s License Show off your vehicle when you sign up! Go outside and take these pictures to upload during the sign-up process: - Front - Back (with license plate visible) - Driver’s side exterior - Passenger’s side exterior - Cargo area/trunk interior BIT.LY Box Truck Drivers Wanted! Apply Now

FRAYT Sponsored Work on your own schedule, earn extra income, and get paid by the next day! FRAYT logistics is seeking box truck drivers who are ambitious and dependable, to hire as independent contractors. We offer customers top notch service by matching their shipping needs with vehicles ready to pick up and deliver orders with our dash, scheduled, and multi-stop service offerings (a platform similar to Uber, but for business delivery). You’ll receive local loads when you want to work, with our non-forced dispatch. We initiate payments to our contractors within 24 hours! Apply here: https://www.frayt.com/box-trucks Requirements: - 21 years or older to use the FRAYT platform - 12’-26’ Box Truck/Straight Truck - Lift gate preferred - Pallet jack recommended - Operating Authority - DOT Number - Minimum required commercial insurance FRAYT.COM Wanted: Box Truck Drivers Apply Now
